i was pissed when he got reworked having enjoyed playing him so much, first main , first champion i got a penta on back when his sheild was insanely op, but now i just just play him top and build him like this and and ascend to op tank status the majority of games i play. hes still thoroughly enjoyable to play, he will just never work with that old morde build. if his w was a flat ms buff and not situational he could easily ascend to garen status.

now i main urgot and morde lel, both the least picked champs at .5%, plz dont butcher urgot further rito.
